        "85 completed line breaks (more than England's 82) showed Croatia's ability to progress the ball. GVARDIOL from CB (16 completed line breaks) was excellent in build-up",
        "BATURINA's goal at 35' and MUSA's at 49' showed Croatia can hurt any team — both came from quick, precise passing combinations exploiting England's momentary defensive lapses"
