      "weaknesses": [
        "xG of 0.82 from 10 shots tells the story — only 5 on target across 90 minutes. Croatia created danger but lacked the clinical quality to convert opportunities",
        "Conceded 4 goals despite decent defensive shape — individual errors and the inability to deal with KANE's movement and BELLINGHAM's late runs proved fatal",
        "MODRIC subbed at 58' with Croatia at 1-2 — losing their creative engine coincided with losing shape and conceding BELLINGHAM's goal immediately after",
        "Croatia's high pressing (295 pressures, 50 direct — most of any team in this match) ultimately drained energy and left gaps England exploited on transition"
